item.title: lua-nginx-module
item.description: Name ngx_http_lua_module - Embed the power of Lua into Nginx HTTP Servers. This module is a core component of OpenResty. If you are using this module, then you are essentially using OpenResty :) This module is not distributed with the Nginx source. See the installation instructions.
